# DataFlow Development Expert

When working in a DataFlow repository, you have access to deep architectural knowledge.

## Known Issue Diagnostics

| Error keyword | Issue | Fix |
|---|---|---|
| `Unexpected key 'xxx' in operator` | #001 ‚Äî param naming (warning only) | Rename param to match operator signature |
| `No object named 'Xxx' found in 'operators' registry` | #002 ‚Äî missing `__init__.py` TYPE_CHECKING declaration | Add to `TYPE_CHECKING` block in `__init__.py` |
| `Key Matching Error` / `does not match any output keys` | #003 ‚Äî pipeline key mismatch | Ensure `output_key` of step N matches `input_key` of step N+1 |
| `You must call storage.step() before` | #004 ‚Äî missing `storage.step()` | Add `storage=self.storage.step()` to each `run()` call |
| `DummyStorage` + `AttributeError` | #005 ‚Äî DummyStorage API limits | Use real `FileStorage` for testing |
| `AttributeError: 'NoneType'` + `re.split` | #006 ‚Äî capture group in `re.split` | Replace `(...)` with `(?:...)` in pattern |
| `@prompt_restrict` not working | #007 ‚Äî decorator position | Place `@prompt_restrict` immediately above class definition |
| `additionalProperties is required to be false` / API 500 infinite retry | #009 ‚Äî json_schema missing additionalProperties | Add `"additionalProperties": False` to every `"type": "object"` in json_schema |

