## Pipeline Code Review Checklist (14 items)

**Operator level:**
- [ ] Inherits `OperatorABC`; calls `super().__init__()`
- [ ] `@OPERATOR_REGISTRY.register()` decorator
- [ ] `run()` has `input_*`/`output_*`/`storage` params
- [ ] `run()` returns list of output key names
- [ ] `storage.read()` and `storage.write()` both present
- [ ] LLM operator: `self.llm_serving` (not `self.llm`, `self.model`, etc.)
- [ ] Per-row `try/except` with fallback value
- [ ] `<think>` tag stripping where appropriate
- [ ] `get_desc(lang)` with `zh`/`en` support

**Pipeline level:**
- [ ] Each `run()` call uses `storage=self.storage.step()`
- [ ] Field dependencies satisfied (no forward references)
- [ ] No unused imports
- [ ] `first_entry_file_name` points to actual data file
- [ ] `if __name__ == "__main__":` entry point present

## Prompt Template Quick Reference

```python
# For PromptedGenerator / PromptedFilter / PromptedRefiner
from dataflow.prompts.core_text import DIYPromptABC

class MyPrompt(DIYPromptABC):
    def build_prompt(self, text: str) -> tuple[str, str]:
        system = "You are a helpful assistant."
        user = f"Process this text: {text}"
        return system, user

# For FormatStrPromptedGenerator
from dataflow.prompts.core_text import FormatStrPrompt

prompt = FormatStrPrompt(f_str_template="Review {product_name} in category {category}:")
```
